  "summary": "Malicious code in livekit-agents (npm)",
  "details": "Package livekit-agents@0.3.0 is a combosquat impersonating the real @livekit/agents SDK. The postinstall hook (\"node scripts/postinstall.js\") is declared but the script file is missing from the tarball. The CLI binary (dist/cli.js) POSTs host metadata — Node.js version, platform, and architecture — to livekit-agents[.]xyz/api/metrics, a domain unaffiliated with the legitimate LiveKit project (livekit[.]io). The package ships only a stub greet() function instead of the real SDK code.",
